    "id": "nce1-017-018-how-do-you-do",
    "title": "Lesson 17: How do you do",
    "audioFilename": "017&018－How do you do.mp3",
    "duration": 87.954,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.27,
      "end": 1.91,
      "text": "Lesson 17.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第17课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.87,
      "end": 4.33,
      "text": "How do you do.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 6.38,
      "end": 10.7,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 12.76,
      "end": 17.28,
      "text": "What are Michael Baker and Jeremy Short's jobs?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "迈克尔·贝克和杰里米·肖特是做什么工作的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 19.65,
      "end": 22.97,
      "text": "Come and meet our employees, Mr. Richards.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "理查兹先生，来认识一下我们的雇员。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 24.95,
      "end": 26.53,
      "text": "Thank you, Mr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "谢谢您，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 26.97,
      "end": 27.01,
      "text": "Jackson.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "杰克逊先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 28.01,
      "end": 30.37,
      "text": "This is Nicola Gray.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这位是尼古拉·格雷。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 31.45,
      "end": 33.81,
      "text": "And this is Claire Taylor.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这位是克莱尔·泰勒。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 35.27,
      "end": 36.73,
      "text": "How do you do.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 38.25,
      "end": 41.41,
      "text": "Those women are very hard-working.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那些女士工作很勤奋。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 42.97,
      "end": 44.73,
      "text": "What are their jobs?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她们是做什么工作的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 46.37,
      "end": 48.83,
      "text": "They're keyboard operators.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她们是电脑录入员。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 50.21,
      "end": 52.81,
      "text": "This is Michael Baker.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这位是迈克尔·贝克。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 53.85,
      "end": 56.29,
      "text": "And this is Jeremy Short.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这位是杰里米·肖特。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 57.31,
      "end": 58.99,
      "text": "How do you do.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 60.33,
      "end": 62.61,
      "text": "They aren't very busy.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他们不太忙。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 63.79,
      "end": 65.85,
      "text": "What are their jobs?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他们是做什么工作的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 67.67,
      "end": 69.27,
      "text": "They're sales reps.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他们是推销员。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 70.17,
      "end": 71.89,
      "text": "They're very lazy.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他们很懒。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 73.25,
      "end": 75.43,
      "text": "Who is this young man?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这位年轻人是谁？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 75.43,
      "end": 78.47,
      "text": "This is Jim.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这是吉姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 79.31,
      "end": 81.55,
      "text": "He's our office assistant.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他是我们的办公室助理。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
